</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_61_r2l2"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>Heincʒ<ex>en</ex></expan> von Redwıcʒ <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> in <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_61_r2l3"><expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſloſſen</expan> geſant habt / das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd laſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_61_r2l4">eẅch <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ vns <expan>H<ex>eincʒ</ex></expan> von Redwicʒ neẅlıch <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_61_r2l5">geſchıkt hat darauf wır Jm ʒu <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex>umb</expan> <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_61_r2l6"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . ſein vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> wır eẅch <expan>hıerınn<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>abſchr<ex>ift</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_61_r2l7"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſloſſen</expan> <expan>ſende<ex>n</ex></expan> / Daran Jr wol mugt <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan> . Als wır <expan>hoffe<ex>n</ex></expan> . daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_61_r2l8">wır Jm gleıch vnd gnugſamlıch <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . Vnd <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_61_r2l9">wır eẅch mıt fleıſʒ . Jr wellt mıt Jm reden vnd Jn <expan>vnd<ex>er</ex>rıchten</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_61_r2l10">daʒ er ſıch des <expan>benüg<ex>en</ex></expan> laſſe . Deẅht Jn <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> daʒ er <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_61_r2l11">ıht ʒe <expan>ſprech<ex>en</ex></expan> hett / <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır Jm <expan>freẅntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_61_r2l12">an den <expan>ſtett<ex>en</ex></expan> da wır das pılleıch tun <expan>ſull<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Denn wa wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_61_r2l14">eẅch lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_61_r2l13"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ij<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> Egıdij </ab>
</div>
<div type="cedula"><ab facs="#facs_61_r2l15">Cettula <expan>Jnt<ex>er</ex>cluſa</expan> / Auch tun wır eẅch ʒe wıſſen / daʒ vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_61_r2l16">
<add><ab facs="#facs_61_r1l1">von den <expan>Carteẅſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_61_r1l2">bey vns </ab></add> fürbracht ıſt / daʒ dıe dreẅ pferd . dıe Heıncʒ von Redwıcʒ ge = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_61_r2l17"><expan>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> hat . Jr ſein . <expan>Bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅch / daʒ Jr Jn darinn <expan>fürderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_61_r2l18">vnd <expan>beholff<ex>en</ex></expan> wellt ſein als wır eẅch wol getrawen . daʒ Jn dıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_61_r2l19"><expan>wıd<ex>er</ex>kert</expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> . das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır <expan>ſunderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vmb eẅch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dıenen</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_61" id="30v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> von <expan>Kocheb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>,
                                <expan>amptm<ex>an</ex></expan> zu Koburg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad,</ex></expan> als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und <expan>Heincz<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        von Redwicz <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> in <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>slossen</expan> gesant habt, das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> und lassen ewch
                                <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz uns
                            <expan>H<ex>eincz</ex></expan> von Redwicz newlich
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> geschikt hat, darauf wir im zu
                                <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex>umb</expan>
<expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein und
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> wir ewch <expan>hierinn<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>abschr<ex>ift</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>slossen</expan>
<expan>sende<ex>n</ex></expan>, daran ir wol mugt
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan>, als wir
                        <expan>hoffe<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz wir im gleich und gnugsamlich
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Und <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewch mit fleisz, ir wellt mit im reden
                        und in <expan>und<ex>er</ex>richten</expan>, daz er sich des
                                <expan>benüg<ex>en</ex></expan> lasse. Dewht in
                                <expan>ab<ex>er,</ex></expan> daz er <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        zu uns iht ze <expan>sprech<ex>en</ex></expan> hett,
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir im <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> sein an den <expan>stett<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                        da wir das pilleich tun <expan>sull<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Denn wa wir ewch
                        lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Egidii. </ab>
</div>
<div type="cedula">
<ab>Cettula <expan>int<ex>er</ex>clusa</expan><lb/>Auch tun wir ewch ze wissen,
                        daz uns <add>von den <expan>cartews<ex>er</ex>n</expan> bey uns</add>
                        fürbracht ist, daz die drew pferd, die Heincz von Redwicz
                                ge<expan>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> hat, ir sein.
                            <expan>Bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewch, daz ir in darinn
                                <expan>fürderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>beholff<ex>en</ex></expan> wellt sein, als wir ewch wol getrawen,
                        daz in die <expan>wid<ex>er</ex>kert</expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>. Das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>sunderl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> umb ewch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
